info.interactivesystems.gamificationengine.entities.rewards

Class PermanentReward

  • java.lang.Object
    • info.interactivesystems.gamificationengine.entities.rewards.Reward
      • info.interactivesystems.gamificationengine.entities.rewards.PermanentReward
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Achievement, Badge

    @Entity
public abstract class PermanentReward
extends Reward
    Permanent rewards are rewards that can be earned only once. These are for example an achievement or a badge. If a player has such an reward she/he may reach the goal again but doesn't get the reward one more time.
